					<head>Commentary</head>
					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597" rend="visible">
						<summary>The commentary of Japheth ben Ali ha-Levi on the book of Proverbs. </summary>
						<textLang mainLang="ara" otherLangs="he">Hebrew, Arabic </textLang>
						<msItem n="0" rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597">
							<locus from="1r" to="132v"/>
							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Perush Mishle </title>
							<title xml:lang="he">פרוש משלי</title>
							<author key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961">
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961" xml:lang="en">Japheth ben Ali, ha-Levi,‏ active 10th century  </persName>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961" xml:lang="he">יפת בן עלי, הלוי</persName>
							</author>
							<note>
								<p>Contains the Hebrew biblical text, written in Arabic characters and provided with vowel-points and accents in red ink, and accompanied by Yefet's Arabic translation and commentary. </p>
								<p>Comments on chapters: 2:1-3:5, 3:13-18, 22-32, 4:1-19, 23-27, 7:1-8:9, 8:32-9:5, 10:1-4, 8-20, 25-28, 11:5-7, 12-26, 12:5-13:7, 13:11-14:16, 14:24-15:22, 16:3-5, 12-26, 27-31, 17:5-6, 15-16, 24-26, 18:2-19:3, 19:7-15, 20-29, 20:12-28, 21:8-21, 22:5-24:14, 27:8-20, 29:11-23, 31:1-29. </p>
							</note>
							<listBibl>
								<bibl>
									<ref target="Wechsler_2003" type="page">283-310</ref>
								</bibl>
							</listBibl>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
